channel.description:
[center] [IMG]http://i49.tinypic.com/2wpnf53.png[/img][/center]
[size=12pt]Introduction[/size]
Hi my name is Saeed, I've been playing RPSP's for a good 3-4 years now, on and off. I've been in quite a few development teams and i know my way around. at the moment what I'm looking for is a dedicated team of developers to come and join my project. I already have the most important things.
[size=14pt]What/Who I'm looking for[/size]
I'm looking for skilled Java server developers that implement with ease the features I want the server to have. I need a team to take a decent base, stabilise it and work together to introduce and maintain the features the server needs. You need to be at a mature age and work with one another in the development team. You need to be able to understand general problems, fix bugs, errors ect ect you need to have experience in coding not that youve followed a couple tutorials and think you a big shot coder.
Current Set-up
* Website - Vbulletin(Paid For) With Prestigescape.com Domain * VPS Server (Windows) * 6GHz Processor * 16GB RAM * 100GB SSD Storage * Unlimited Bandwidth (Low Ping / DDoS Resistant)
If you're interested then please either send me a PM or add my on skype (Khaos.ps) or reply to this thread with the following information.
Coders We Have:
Game Coder : Zeropointx Web Dev : Xorex Web Dev : Jaded
Im Looking For More Coders Who Can Share Exp! Not Us Having To Teach You!
